  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "Our findings show various explanation attributes that can significantly contribute to the explanation quality, capability, and end users' perception system (Lipton, 1990).",
    "In Fig. 2, the \"Attributes\" refer to the explanation attributes that should be present in XAI systems as per our empirical investigation.",
    "We argue that these attributes can contribute to the \"explanation quality dimensions\" proposed by Haque et al. (2023), which are based on the information quality dimensions of Wixom and Todd (2005).",
    "We argue that the attributes we have shown in this research can contribute to the two proposed explanation quality dimensions, namely, \"format\" and \"completeness,\" that eventually impact the user's beliefs, AI adoption, and intention to use AI systems (Eagly & Chaiken, 1993; Fazio & Olson, 2007; Haque et al., 2023).",
    "The empirical insights in our research show that users with appropriate explanations are more prone to perceive the system as transparent, trustworthy, and less biased, ultimately leading to informed decision-making."
  ],
